data.description:
Beautiful corner lot home in over than an acre, in a peaceful  premium location with beautiful scenic views close of vicinity of Bill Gates Smart City Area.
Main house: Nice designed open floorplan with all tile flooring, 9' ceiling, wood cabinetry and stainless steel appliances. Spacious living room, hall, social bathroom and huge family room. Fresh and airy kitchen with walk in pantry.  4 bedrooms w/ bathroom and walk in closet in each one. The huge master bedroom with a nice jacuzzi inside. 
Guest house,:  2 bedrooms, 1 bath, Kitchen, laundry , dining room and living room.
No HOA, no water bill and plenty of space to park toys on and off the concrete.

Great Property for a business owner that needs space, safety & comfort at reasonable value, do not lost long.
